msgstr "当前密码无效。"

msgid "New password length should be between %d and %d characters."
msgstr "新密码长度必须在 %d 到 %d 个字符之间。"

msgid "New password should only include alpha-numeric characters and symbols."
msgstr "新密码只能包含字母、数字和符号。"

msgid "New passwords do not match."
msgstr "两次输入的新密码不一致。"

msgid "Are you sure you want to delete this character?\nThis action is permanent, and you will not be able to recover or use this character again.\n"
msgstr "你确定要删除这个角色吗？\n此操作是永久性的，删除后你将无法恢复或再次使用该角色。\n"

