msgid "Welcome to Source of Mana!\n\nYou're currently playing the web version, which may run slower and isn't as stable as the downloadable versions.\n\nThis version is mainly here to showcase the game.\nFor the best experience, we recommend using the native client found on our itch.io page (Available on Windows, Linux, macOS, and Android).\n"
msgstr "欢迎来到 Mana 之源！\n\n你当前正在游玩网页版，它的运行速度可能更慢，稳定性也不如可下载的客户端版本。\n\n这个版本主要用于展示游戏内容。\n若想获得最佳体验，我们推荐你使用 itch.io 页面上的原生客户端版本（支持 Windows、Linux、macOS 和 Android）。\n"

msgid "Welcome to Source of Mana!\n\nThis is an open-source MMORPG and still a work in progress. You're welcome to explore, test, and enjoy the current features.\n\nWe're also always looking for contributors!\nIf you'd like to get involved in development, design, writing, or testing, feel free to join our community.\nOtherwise, have fun and thank you for playing!\n"
msgstr "欢迎来到 Mana 之源！\n\n这是一款开源 MMORPG，目前仍在持续开发中。欢迎你来探索、测试并体验现阶段的内容。\n\n我们也一直在寻找新的贡献者！\n如果你想参与开发、设计、文案或测试，欢迎加入我们的社区。\n无论如何，祝你玩得开心，也感谢你的游玩！\n"

msgid "You are dead."
msgstr "你死了。"

msgid "We regret to inform you that your character was killed in battle."
msgstr "很遗憾地通知你，你的角色在战斗中阵亡了。"

msgid "You are not that alive anymore."
msgstr "你现在已经不怎么活着了。"

msgid "Game Over!"
msgstr "游戏结束！"

msgid "Insert coin to continue."
msgstr "请投币继续。"

msgid "No, kids. Your character did not really die. It... err... went to a better place."
msgstr "别担心，孩子。你的角色并不是真的死了。它……呃……去了一个更好的地方。"

msgid "You've outlived your usefulness. Mommy now wants you to help with supper."
msgstr "你的作用已经到头了。妈妈现在要你去帮忙准备晚饭。"

msgid "I guess this did not run too well."
msgstr "看来这次运行得不太顺利。"

msgid "You are no more."
msgstr "你已经不复存在。"

msgid "You have ceased to be."
msgstr "你已经停止存在。"

msgid "You've expired and gone to meet your maker."
msgstr "你已寿终正寝，去见你的造物主了。"

msgid "You're a stiff."
msgstr "你已经是一具僵硬的尸体了。"

msgid "Bereft of life, you rest in peace."
msgstr "失去生命后，你终于安息了。"

msgid "If you weren't so animated, you'd be pushing up the daisies."
msgstr "要不是你刚才还活蹦乱跳，现在早该在地下顶花了。"

msgid "You're off the twig."
msgstr "你已经从枝头掉下去了。"

msgid "You've kicked the bucket."
msgstr "你已经一命呜呼。"

msgid "You are an ex-player."
msgstr "你现在是前玩家了。"

msgid "Right now, you would just love to be resurrected."
msgstr "你现在一定非常想复活。"

msgid "Wait, did I just die?"
msgstr "等等，我刚刚死了吗？"

msgid "What just happened?"
msgstr "刚才发生了什么？"

msgid "I guess you're not the One."
msgstr "看来你并不是那个天选之人。"

msgid "See you in the underworld."
msgstr "冥界见。"

msgid "Try again."
msgstr "再试一次。"

msgid "Don't panic, you're just a bit dead."
msgstr "别慌，你只是稍微死了一点。"

msgid "It's a bit late to start digging your grave, don't you think?"
msgstr "现在才开始给自己挖坟，是不是有点晚了？"

msgid "Program terminated."
msgstr "程序已终止。"

msgid "Mission failed."
msgstr "任务失败。"

msgid "Do you want your possessions identified?"
msgstr "你想鉴定一下自己的遗物吗？"

msgid "Sadly, no trace of you was ever found..."
msgstr "遗憾的是，再也没有人找到过你的踪迹……"

msgid "Annihilated."
msgstr "灰飞烟灭。"

msgid "Dying is easy. Living is harder."
msgstr "死亡很容易，活着更难。"

msgid "Looks like you got your head handed to you."
msgstr "看起来你被打得找不着北了。"

msgid "You screwed up again, dump your body down the tubes and get you another one."
msgstr "你又搞砸了，把这副身体扔进下水道，再换一具吧。"

msgid "You're not dead yet. You're just resting."
msgstr "你还没死，你只是躺着休息一下。"

msgid "Everybody falls the first time."
msgstr "每个人第一次都会倒下。"

msgid "Welcome... to the real world."
msgstr "欢迎……来到真实世界。"

msgid "Fate, it seems, is not without a sense of irony."
msgstr "看来命运也不是毫无讽刺感。"

msgid "There is no spoon."
msgstr "根本没有勺子。"

msgid "One shot, one kill."
msgstr "一枪一个。"

msgid "Some men just want to watch the world burn."
msgstr "有些人只是想看着世界燃烧。"

msgid "You are fulfilling your destiny."
msgstr "你正在完成自己的宿命。"

msgid "Rule #8: Do not die."
msgstr "第 8 条规则：别死。"

msgid "There will be no order, only chaos."
msgstr "不会有秩序，只有混乱。"

msgid "Too bad, get over it."
msgstr "真遗憾，接受现实吧。"

msgid "There's no hope for us here, only death."
msgstr "这里没有希望，只有死亡。"

msgid "Death is the road to awe."
msgstr "死亡是通往敬畏之路。"

msgid "Stop... Stop it!"
msgstr "停下……快停下！"

msgid "Today is a good day to die."
msgstr "今天是个赴死的好日子。"

msgid "Any last words? Oops, too late!"
msgstr "还有什么遗言吗？哦，太晚了！"

msgid "Confusion will be my epitaph."
msgstr "混乱将成为我的墓志铭。"

msgid "KO"
msgstr "击倒"

msgid "GG"
msgstr "GG"

msgid "Better luck next time."
msgstr "下次好运。"

msgid "Everything is a dream."
msgstr "一切都只是一场梦。"

msgid "Oh dear, the RNG is angry with you again."
msgstr "哎呀，随机数女神又生你的气了。"

msgid "Well... That happens, I guess."
msgstr "嗯……这种事嘛，也会发生。"

msgid "That is just part of life-- err, death, I mean."
msgstr "这只是人生的一部分，呃，我是说死亡的一部分。"

msgid "Are you enjoying lying on the ground?"
msgstr "你躺在地上的感觉还舒服吗？"

msgid "Today is not your lucky day, it seems."
msgstr "看来今天不是你的幸运日。"

msgid "Dead already? But you were so young..."
msgstr "这么快就死了？可你还这么年轻……"

msgid "Next time, say thanks when you get off the bus."
msgstr "下次下车的时候记得说谢谢。"

msgid "Walk towards the light."
msgstr "朝着光走去吧。"

msgid "And thus, you return to dust; Fulfilling the prophecy."
msgstr "于是你归于尘土，完成了预言。"

msgid "Do you want your noob certificate now or later?"
msgstr "你的菜鸟证书想现在领还是晚点领？"

msgid "One Tap."
msgstr "一枪爆头。"

msgid "Wasted"
msgstr "报废"

msgid "Critical Existence Failure."
msgstr "存在发生致命错误。"

msgid "If you see an elevator, be sure to push the up button."
msgstr "如果你看到电梯，记得按上行键。"

msgid "Well, that healing item was too awesome to use, anyway..."
msgstr "反正那件治疗道具也好用得舍不得用……"

msgid "Hey hey, I wasn't done yet!"
msgstr "嘿嘿，我还没结束呢！"

msgid "Why you bully me!"
msgstr "你为什么欺负我！"

msgid "The cake is a lie."
msgstr "蛋糕是个谎言。"

msgid "It is good day to be not dead!"
msgstr "今天真是个适合不死的好日子！"

msgid "Well poop. Let's try not dying next time."
msgstr "糟了。下次试着别死吧。"

msgid "Outgunned."
msgstr "火力被压制。"

msgid "If I try to get away, how long until I'm free? And if I don't come back here, will anyone remember me?"
msgstr "如果我试着逃离，要多久才能真正自由？如果我再也回不来了，还会有人记得我吗？"
